---
title: "getAssetOutAmount view (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_valid: load assetInParams, auctionStart
    q_check_valid --> q_return_zero: auctionStart == 0 or expired or timestamp < auctionStart
    q_return_zero --> [*]: return 0
    q_check_valid --> q_clamp_amount: auction is valid at timestamp
    q_clamp_amount --> q_get_price: amount = min(amount, availableBalance)
    q_get_price --> q_compute: _getAssetPrice(assetIn, false)
    q_compute --> [*]: return _getAssetOutAmount(params, price, amount, elapsed, false)

    note right of q_clamp_amount
        INV-001: Amount is clamped to available balance (no revert on excess)
        INV-002: Returns 0 for invalid auctions instead of reverting
        INV-003: Uses non-validating price fetch (view-safe)
    end note
